@drpngx , @satok16 , There is double free happening in hexagon_nn_lib:do_teardowngraph function, which is causing adsp crash and won't let run the test, until next reboot, If anybody unaware, as a work around, comment teardowngraph as this allows to run test once and exit without crash. Next time run the test without reboot.

further working on debugging hexagon_nnlib: teardown graph and remove double free

thanks
